title: Dallas Barr 01 - 03 (1996 - 1998) (Ouash) cbr
description:
Since the beginning of the 21st century, immortality has been a reality. At the rejuvenation clinics of Lord Julius Stileman, anyone can experience the prime years of their youth once more. However, the treatment will cost you everything you own, and the minimum price is one million bucks. Because the treatment only lasts ten years, after the procedure is complete there begins a deadly race against the clock. You will have to rebuild your assets in time to remain immortal, because every ten years it comes down to a simple choice: Your money, or your life.
